        P2-G6 — independent of this task.</item>
      <item>Task 025 (D2-15) — Subject resolution + HTTP client. Sibling in
        P2-G6 — independent of this task.</item>
      <item>Task 026 (D2-16) — `InsightsResponseRenderer` two-path component. DIRECT
        BLOCKING DEPENDENCY. This task is a small extension of 026.</item>
      <item>Task 027 (D2-17) — Clickable citations. Sibling in P2-G6 — also extends
        the renderer (task 026); coordinate via single PR or sequential commits
        within the renderer file to avoid merge conflicts.</item>
      <item>Spec.md Open Decisions row "Insights v1.1 D5" — the design decision
        that motivated this task. R5 chose client-side over server-side.</item>
      <item>Integration brief §4 — response schema definitions for both paths
        (playbook + RAG); `confidence` field shape verification.</item>
    </related-work>
  </context>

