        or use the Wave D7 synthetic test entities and override the response
        in browser DevTools to set `confidence: 0.4`).
      - Confirm badge appears alongside the response.

      Negative (badge absent):
      - Trigger a high-confidence response (or override to `confidence: 0.9`).
      - Confirm no badge in DOM.

      Boundary (badge absent at exact threshold):
      - Override to `confidence: 0.6` (exact threshold).
      - Confirm no badge (0.6 is NOT &lt; 0.6).

      Both paths:
      - Verify the badge appears for both `path: "playbook"` and `path: "rag"`
        when confidence is below threshold.

      Capture browser DevTools screenshots / console traces for task notes.
    </step>
    <step order="9" name="Verify Acceptance Criteria">
